channel.title: 3b+ main account givaway to my server voters/players!
channel.description: Hello! after playing runescape for about 4 years i think its finally time to hang up the ropes now that i have gotten hooked on rsps creation.[size=12pt][b] So i will be giving away my account to the players or general voters of the server. there are 2 ways to win the account. either voting for my server and taking a screen shot at on google or just playing my server in general. This wount let me put the link up so ill tell you its called "Runelive" and it is under the serverlist and it is ranked 9th right now[/b][/size] Now here are the pictures of the account. [URL=http://min.us/lj1RaK][IMG]http://i.min.us/jj1RaK.png[/img][/URL] [URL=http://min.us/ljwPRU][IMG]http://i.min.us/jjwPRU.png[/img][/URL] [URL=http://min.us/ljwSac][IMG]http://i.min.us/jjwSac.png[/img][/URL] GOOD LUCK TO ALL! http://www.rune-server.org/top.php?act=detail&sid=4219
